	<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>To process, say, all *.txt files in the current directory:</p>
<blockquote>
<div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre>vim *.txt
:set hidden
:bufdo %s/\r$//e
:bufdo %s/\r/ /eg
:xa</pre></div>
</div>

</blockquote>]]></content:encoded>
